Strengths

- Free and easy to use
- Lots of training resources available
- Strong user community to get your answers

Limitations

- Unlike other visualization tools, one needs to know python programming to use matplotlib
- Not very well suited for some complex time series plots

Alternative options

The alternative options are-

- Tableau
- Bokesh
- GGplot2
- Bokeh
- Matlab

